# Repo-root .dockerignore — applied when build context is the repo root
# (used by apps/web/Dockerfile).
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.venv
**/venv
**/dist
**/build
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/.cache
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.DS_Store
.git
.github
docs
*.md
!README.md
!apps/api/README.md
!apps/web/README.md
